			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Zuauna le khemna ka zat loh nadingin hong huh inla, a haulua lo, a zawnglua loin hong bawl inla, ka khamkhop zah lian bek an hong pia in.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Haulua leng nang hong nialin, “Topa i cih kua ahi hiam?” kong ci kha ding a, zawnglua leuleu leng mi’ na guksakin ka Pasian’ min kong daisak khazel ding hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sila khat a topa kiangah gensia kei in; amah in nang hong gensia-in gimna na thuakkha ding hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A pate samsia-in a min a daisak, a nute a phat lo mi pawlkhat om hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Amaute a nin mahmah hinapi-in amau’ muhna-ah siang a kisa mahmah mi pawlkhat om hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Mihoih pha mahmahin a kingaihsun, a kiliansak mahmah mi pawlkhat om hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> A ha uh namsau tawh a kibang gam sung mizawngte a netum, mi cimawhte a liaktum mi pawlkhat om hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Vot in tanu nih nei a, khat in, “Hong pia in,” ci a, a khat in zong, “Hong pia in,” mah ci veve hi. “Phazo ta,” a ci ngei lo nam thum om a, eh! li hi zaw:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Han khuk, taciing numei, tui a deih tawntung lei keu, le a kisumit zo lo meikuang.",
