			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Vanah musane a leentheihna zia, suangpi tungah gul a pai theihna zia, tuipi tungah teembaw a pai theihna zia, le nungak tangval a kingaihna zia.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> A citak lo zi hih bangin gamta hi: Midang tawh khialin tua ciangin kisilsiang a, “Khialhna bangmah gamta kei ing,” ci khem hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Leitung mi khempeuh in a thuakzawh loh thu thum, eh! thu li om a,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> sila khat kumpi a suah ciang, mihai khat in a duh bangbang a nek zawh ciang,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> a muhthadahhuai numei khat in pasal a neih ciang, nasem numeino in a tonu’ za a suan ciang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> A neu mahmah ganhing nam li leitungah om a, ahi zongin a pil penpente ahi hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Miksite: A hat het lo ganhing hinapi-in khuakhal sungin a nek ding uh kholzo uh hi.",
