			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kauphete: Kumpi nei lo napi-in a kituak diamdiamin hontat thei uh hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Innhikte: Khut sunga tawizawh ganhing hilel napi-in kumpi inn sungah tengzo uh hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> A gamtatna i et ciangin a thupi suak mahmah thum, eh! li om hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Humpinelkai: Ganhing lak pan a hatpen kuamah a kihta lo.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Aklui: A kihisak pai kuankuan. Keeltal: A kihisak pai gangan. Kumpipa: A mite’ mai-ah a pai lanlan.",
