			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Phalvak tungin zingtho a, annek ding teng limtakin bawlin a nasem numeite’ sep dingteng a vaihawmsak hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Amah in leitang hoih penpen zong a, a thalawhsa sum tawh a leenggui lo ding a lei hi.",
